      <h1 class="title-headings fade-in">Technographics in Your Business</h1>
      <h2 class="title-subheading fade-in" >Knowing Your Client’s Trigger</h2>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 contact-side align-items-center text-center">
            <p class="contact-para fade-in">When you know your client, you know what makes them tick. Technographic Segmentation,
               better known as technographics,<span class="color-highlight-light"> profiles</span> your target accounts based on their technology stack.
               This analysis of statistical data measures and categorizes<span class="color-highlight-light"> ownership</span>, patterns of
                 <span class="color-highlight-light">usage</span> and <span class="color-highlight-light">attitude</span> towards
               your solution, providing a precise <span class="color-highlight-light">360 degree perspective</span> of your potential buyer. Technographic Intelligence
               offers not just a peek but a deep understanding of technology infrastructure. </p>
        </div>
        <span class="color-highlight-light"> </span>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <h2 class="title-subheading fade-in">Here's why you should be interested in uncovering data ecosystems</h2>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Planning a Market Strategy</h3>
                <p> The prospect’s solution stack guides you in planning effective campaigns and outreach strategies,
                  translating into building the best selling opportunity in response to your understanding of their
                  real needs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Amplified Efficiency </h3>
                <p>Through targeted prospecting, technographics provide an accurate representation of your Total
                  Accessible Market (TAM) so your salespeople spend their time selling, rather than finding people to sell.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Knowing the Customer</h3>
                <p>By knowing their technology stack, you can speak to them with intricate consciousness of how they function, 
                  their pain points and your solution's value adds to them, making research the key in closing  deals.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Greater Customisation</h3>
                <p>Once you lock your target market, technographics help you tailor your content for them, by creating proactive,
                   result oriented advertisements or messages about solutions your potential client needs. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Leverage Data for Competitive Insight</h3>
                <p>A glimpse into the real market, the solutions being used and the amount spent on them gives you the
                   upper hand against your pool of competitors. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Customer Retention</h3>
                <p>Use the insight from the data to forecast the market, drive product development according to demand
                  and connect the dots between your releases and customer needs.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="row fade-in">
        <p class="contact-para">Technographics places you between potential conversations and practical insights,
